snippet.title: Yogurt Commercial 3: Change Your Life
snippet.description:
Yogurt Commercial 3 launches May 3 on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1319790/Yogurt_Commercial_3/

Change your job, change your life. Change into a Yogurt Commercial actor and get shot out of a cannon. Who's that narrating this teaser? Oh yeah that's Bob. He's going to explain what this game is all about, just listen.
